collections​
商店的全部商品分类。
迭代访问 collections​
您可以迭代collections以构建分类的列表。
Code
Data
1
2
3
4
{{#each collections as |collection|}}
{{{ link_to collection.title collection.url }}}
{{/each}}

Output
1
2
3
4
<a href="/collections/empty">Empty</a>
<a href="/collections/featured-potions">Featured potions</a>
<a href="/collections/freebies">Freebies</a>
<a href="/collections/frontpage">Home page</a>
从模板获取
collections_all
